reviewText: I've wanted a copy of this film from the time I first saw it on A&E. Now, thanks to this great seller, I have it. DVD itself, was brand new in the box, and a very clean copy. I am very happy, and would definitely do business with this seller again.

This is a great mystery with an intelligent story line but the real pleasure is the cast.  Gene Wilder -- wonderfual.  Each of the others terrific. The setting, cars and clothing are almost as good as the history lesson. And it's fun.  I highly recommend it for those of us sick of 12 year old mentality TV.
